 binary model, makes the stability of this star unusual among other active\nstars. It suggests a stable magnetic field orientation where spots are always\ngenerated at about the same location on the surface of the star.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Sep 2001 18:23:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
